FBIS3-12338 "drnes039_n_94014" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 LEBANON 28 Feb Declared Day of Mourning for Victims NC2702173794 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 27 Feb 94 NC2702173794 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Lebanon will observe a day of mourning tomorrow, Monday, in a show of public grief over the death of innocent victims in the criminal bombing at Sayyidat al-Najat Church.
